description:
This tutorial shows you the basics video editing in photoshop

You need just a photoshop cs6

The duration of the course of about 31 minutes

If you want to learn the technique of video processing then you should sign up for my course

And please, after viewing the course leave your review. I need your opinion.

If you liked this course, I advise you to sign up for my new course . There you will find lots of interesting information for you!
title: Working with Video in Photoshop CS6
